ts/Bob-Vylan">Bob Vylan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Wargasm">Wargasm</a> 、Jenny（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lets-eat-grandma">Let&#39;s Eat Grandma</a> ）等。</p><p>根据一份新闻稿，《The Drain》“证明了这两个强大的音乐实体之间的共生创造力，利用它们各自独特的声音特征，创造出精心制作的、独特的沉重单曲。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/bad-omens-interview-2023-noah-sebastian-just-pretend-3432162">去年，《Bad Omens》接受了<em>NME</em>采访，</a>塞巴斯蒂安在第三张专辑《The Death of Peace of Mind》中公开了他的职业道德。 “我觉得在过去的一年半里我真的找到了自己，”他告诉<em>《NME》</em> 。 “在大流行期间，[我]真的很想提高自己的声音，因为我总是对自己非常挑剔。 [这是]这些因素的结合，让身体变得更好、更健康、睡得更好、吃得更好。”</p><p> “因为我能够用我的声音做事，这就是为什么这张唱片如此专注于声音。制作是围绕声乐、歌词、主题和你可以在声乐中传达的情感的细微差别而建立的，”他补充道。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bad-omens-cancel-summer-uk-and-european-tour-dates-due-to-extreme-burnout-3759046">《Bad Omens》因“极度倦怠”而取消夏季英国和欧洲巡演日期的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Hoobastank 的《The Reason》在 Spotify 上获得了 10 亿次播放量https://www.nme.com/news/music/hoobastanks-the-reason-earns-one-billion-streams-on-spotify-3759050?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=hoobastanks-the-reason-earns-one- Spotify 上的十亿流媒体Anagricel DuranThu, 23 May 2024 19:35:00 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockSpotify https://www.nme.com/?p=3759050 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Hoobastank 乐队在 2004 年公告牌音乐奖颁奖典礼上摆出姿势拍照。 （弗兰克·米塞洛塔/福克斯通过盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这一里程碑发生在该赛道成立 20 周年之际</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hoobastanks-the-reason-earns-one-billion-streams-on-spotify-3759050">Hoobastank 的《The Reason》在 Spotify 上获得了 10 亿流媒体播放量，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Hoobastank 乐队在 2004 年公告牌音乐奖颁奖典礼上摆出姿势拍照。 （弗兰克·米塞洛塔/福克斯通过盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Hoobastank-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Hoobastank">Hoobastank</a>的歌曲《The Reason》已在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/spotify">Spotify</a>上突破 10 亿次播放量，加入了<a href="/artists/Ed-Sheeran">Ed Sheeran</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Drake">Drake</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Coldplay">Coldplay</a>等音乐人的行列。</p><p> “The Reason”于2004年1月26日发行，作为乐队第二张同名专辑中的单曲。这首力量民谣是 Hoobastank 在商业上最成功的单曲。发行后，该曲目在美国 Billboard Hot 100 排行榜上名列第二，在美国现代摇滚曲目排行榜上名列第一。</p><p>第二年，这首歌为乐队赢得了两项<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>年度歌曲提名和最佳流行二重唱或团体演唱提名。随着《The Reason》迎来 20 岁生日，流媒体播放量突破 10 亿次里程碑。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Hoobastank - The Reason（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fV4DiAyExN0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：原因" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/5B5eTk7DF8KVp1zpQoY1XY?utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>吉他手丹·埃斯特林 (Dan Estrin) 在一份声明中谈到这一成就时说道：“多么令人惊叹的时刻。和儿时最好的朋友一起创造一些东西，然后看着它发展成一场失控的野火，这绝对是超现实的。”</p><p>他继续说道：“我们谁也没想到会发生这样的事，有时感觉就像一场梦。知道“The Reason”对于世界上这么多人的意义是一种难以形容的、自豪的、激动人心的感觉。我非常感激并意识到我们是多么幸运。我们已经在世界各地演奏过它。当他们一起唱歌时看到每个人的脸是无价的。谢谢世界。”</p><p> “十亿很酷，但一万亿就太棒了！”歌手道格·罗布补充道。 “一边开玩笑，我对这首歌的生活和继续拥有的生活感到惊讶和惊讶。它是如此酷，以至于现在已经编织成新一代的音乐品味。让我们再去十亿！”</p><p> Hoobastank是加入Spotify十亿溪俱乐部的最新乐队。其他具有曲目在流媒体平台上超过十亿溪流的音乐家包括<a href="/artists/Maroon-5">Maroon 5</a> ， <a href="/artists/Ariana-Grande">Ariana Grande</a> ， <a href="/artists/Bruno-Mars">Bruno Mars</a> ， <a href="/artists/Bad-Bunny">Bad Bunny</a> ， <a href="/artists/Justin-Bieber">Justin Bieber</a> ， <a href="/artists/Dua-Lipa">Dua Lipa</a>等。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2Aal1CrWjm/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886